    <description>06/18/24 - PE - Added new field mappings to update fields on the onboarding records,
07/3/24 - PE - Updated flow to only populate SaaS Activation field on onboarding if funnel stage is &quot;Activated&apos;
07/11/24 - PE Removed logic to only find Onboarding Record where SaaS Activation Date is null
07/16/24 - PE - Updated entry criteria to formula so the flow is fired when a new school object is created
08/01/24 - PE - Added the old fields to trigger the automation
05/21/2024 - LK - Added Logic to update Account fields - Saas OBE AE Owner or Saas Activation AE Owner when OBE Dates or Activation dates are updated.
05/22/2025 - AC - Removed references to the Account Status field.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forD_SaaSActivationDateStamp</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
ISPICKVAL({!$Record.SaaS_Activation_Funnel_Stage_2024__c}, &quot;Activated&quot;),
{!$Record.SaaS_Activation_Date_2024__c},
NULL
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>SaaSFunnelStartDate</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>DATEVALUE({!$Record.SaaS_Funnel_Start_Date__c})+1</expression>
    </formulas>
    <interviewLabel>SaaS Activation Funnel Updates - School Object to Onboarding {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
